com.redhat.rhn.domain.credentials

Class Credentials

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.redhat.rhn.domain.BaseDomainHelper
      • com.redhat.rhn.domain.credentials.Credentials

  • public class Credentials
extends BaseDomainHelper
    Credentials - Java representation of the table SUSECREDENTIALS. This table contains pairs of credentials used for communicating with 3rd party systems, e.g. API usernames and keys.
